DataElement.preferredName: Notification Administration Reuse Template Study Activity Repeat Frequency Ratio ISO21090.RTO.INT.NONNEG,PQ.TIME.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: An administrative activity defined at the global library level that represents the communication of a message to a recipient. EXAMPLE(S): An alert sent to a study PI that the study has reached 75% of target subject accrual. A ratio representing the number of occurrences of an activity within a given time period. EXAMPLE(S): Once per 12 hours, 2 times per day
